{"id":95266,"date":"2019-02-26T17:19:14","date_gmt":"2019-02-26T17:19:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/?p=95266"},"modified":"2019-02-26T17:28:30","modified_gmt":"2019-02-26T17:28:30","slug":"financial-commission-announces-execution-quality-certification-of-grand-capital","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2019\/02\/26\/financial-commission-announces-execution-quality-certification-of-grand-capital\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Announces Execution Quality Certification of Grand Capital","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">February 26th, 2019, The Financial Commission today announces execution certification for <a href=\"https:\/\/grandcapital.net\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Grand Capital<\/a>, an approved member of the Commission using Verify My Trade, a \u201cvalue-added\u201d service launched in 2018 to promote pricing and execution transparency in the Forex market. Grand Capital becomes the 11th broker member to receive the VMT certification.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/grandcapital.net\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-31594 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/grandcapitallogo-e1512128770629.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"76\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Verified order execution quality<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Following the launch of order execution verification with Verify My Trade (VMT) in September of 2018, Financial Commission broker members continue to apply for certification of their order execution quality as a step to increase transparency regarding execution speed and pricing.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Today, Grand Capital becomes the latest Financial Commission member to have successfully completed the VMT certification, having satisfied all execution quality standards set out for all members of the Commission. Trades can now view the execution audit results for Grand Capital directly on our website, by <a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/grand-capital\/\">clicking here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Check your broker\u2019s status<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">All interested parties can now view the execution audit results for all members of the Financial Commission by visiting our Members page or the profile pages of brokers listed in our Members section. Certified brokers will be highlighted with a unique badge as displayed below.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-86982\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"67\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large.png 793w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large-300x67.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large-768x171.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large-200x45.png 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large-400x89.png 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-large-600x134.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%; padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-87037\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"75\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large.png 981w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-300x75.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-768x192.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-200x50.png 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-400x100.png 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-600x150.png 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/vmt-green-tick-large-800x200.png 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">By clicking on the badge users will navigate to a dedicated webpage for each broker that will indicate the last time an audit was performed, how many orders were analyzed and whether the results satisfied the order execution standards established by VMT.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are interested in using the VMT service or would like more information, please reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.org\">info@financialcommission.org<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>February 26th, 2019, The Financial Commission today announces execution certification for Grand Capital, an approved member of the Commission using Verify My Trade, a \u201cvalue-added\u201d service launched in 2018 to promote pricing and execution transparency in the Forex market. Grand Capital becomes the 11th broker member to receive the VMT certification. &nbsp; &nbsp; Verified order [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":13,"featured_media":31594,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,15,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-95266","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-release","category-press-releases-news-events"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/95266","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/13"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=95266"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/95266\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/31594"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=95266"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=95266"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=95266"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}